Div-u z id="accordion" spremeni class col-md-4 v col-md-12 in pred njega dodaj:

	<div class="col-md-4 col-xs-12 col-sm-12">
          <ul class="nav nav-tabs">
              <li class="active"><a data-toggle="tab" href="#meritve" > MERITVE </a></li>
              <li>
                <a data-toggle=“tab” href="#navodila"> NAVODILA
              </li>
          </ul>
            <div class="tab-content">
              <div class="tab-pane fade in active" id="meritve">

in vso kodo, ki predstavlja meritve "zapri" v div z id="meritve".

Za njim dodaj še kodo
	
    <div class="tab-pane fade" id="navodila">
        <div class="col-xs-12">
               //vstavi besedilo  
        </div>
    </div>
.

V style.css dodaj:

.navodila{
  font: 6px;
}

.tab-content{
  padding: 2em 0;
  border-left: 1px solid #ddd;
  border-right: 1px solid #ddd;
  border-bottom: 1px solid #ddd;
  border-radius: 0px 0px 5px 5px;
}

.nav-tabs li{
  width: 50%;
}

.nav-tabs a{
  color: black;
}

.nav-tabs li a .caret{
  border-top-color: black;
  border-bottom-color: black;
}

ul li .dropdown-toggle{
  margin-right: 0;
}

.dropdown-menu li{
  width: 100%;
  margin: 0;
}

.dropdown-menu li > a:hover, .dropdown-menu li > a:focus, .dropdown-submenu:hover > a{
  background-color: rgb(238, 238, 238);
  color: black;
}

.dropdown-menu > .active > a:hover{
  background-color: rgb(238, 238, 238);
  color: black;
}

.dropdown-menu > .active > a{
  background-color: white;
  color: black;
}.
